Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_scan_chain(25.10)                              report_scan_chain(25.10)

Name
       report_scan_chain - Prints the scan chain information

Syntax
       report_scan_chain

       [-help]

       [-chain <chainName>]

       [-out_file <fileName>]

       [-verbose {true|false}]

       Prints  the  scan chain information. The information includes total bit
       count, wire length of floating, order, and total  scan  chain  segment.
       Tool  automatically calls scanTrace before printing scan chain informa-
       tion.

Parameters
       -chain <chainName>
              Specifies the scan chain name.

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each report_scan_chain parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_scan_chain.

       -out_file <fileName>
              Specifies  the output file name of scan chain. If not specified,
              the tool prints scan  chain  information  in  the  scanChain.rpt
              file.

       -verbose {true|false}
              Prints  out more message that includes each scan chain component
              and wire length between them.

Example
              * The following command writes the chain0 information:

         report_scan_chain -chain chain0 -verbose true

         [1] scan info : chain0

         START: top/hinst_1/inst_1/Z (319.224, 356.952)

         STOP: top/hinst_1/inst_2/SI (236.880, 324.742)

           39.611  ordered top/hinst_1 /inst_1/I

           43.773  ordered top/hinst_1 /reg_1/SI

           ...

           1.036  ordered top/hinst_1 /inst_213/I

           0.300  ordered top/hinst_1 /reg_89/I

           55.773  floating top/hinst_1/inst_2/SI

         scan bits        : 225

         float wire length: 440.295

         order wire length: 390.968

         total wire length: 831.263

